{"word":"G649 - ἀποστέλλω - apostéllō - ap-os-tel'-lo - Put in","slug":"G649","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποστέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apostéllō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-os-tel'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Put in"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9; - apostello&#x0304;</b> - <i>ap-os-tel'-lo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G4724\">G4724</a>; <i>set apart</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>send out</i> (properly on a mission) literally or figuratively: - put in, send (away, forth, out), set [at liberty]."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1821\">G1821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3992\">G3992</a>, <a href=\"#/G5570\">G5570</a>, <a href=\"#/G651\">G651</a>, <a href=\"#/G652\">G652</a>"}]}